rComments: Nice man. It's easy to have a conversation with him. He can be quite boring but since most of the time you're watching student presentations, it's not reason enough to switch sections. He was passionate about issues but like was said, he can go on for a while. Marks fairly/easily.
Instructor was absolutely boring. Keeps talking non-stop. Although he's a nice person he doesn't know how to make policy interesting. I wish I switched to another section. Marks hard as well.
The dryest, most boring professor at the FSW.  His lectures were TERRIBLE - nice guy, but those classes were PURE torture.  Is not engaging or dynamic at all, and lectures consist of text.
Very vague at times. Nice manner but needs to be more concrete when teaching.
